<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CloseClaw — Operating Instructions</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=VT323&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --green:   #00ff41;
  --green2:  #00cc33;
  --amber:   #ffb000;
  --red:     #ff3333;
  --dim:     #1a1a1a;
  --mid:     #0d0d0d;
  --bg:      #070707;
  --border:  #1f3320;
  --text:    #c8ffd4;
  --muted:   #4a6b4e;
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* scanlines */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(
    0deg,
    transparent,
    transparent 2px,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 2px,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 4px
  );
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1000;
}

/* phosphor glow on text */
body::after {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, rgba(0,255,65,0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 999;
}

/* ── LAYOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.layout {
  display: flex;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* ── SIDEBAR ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

nav {
  width: 260px;
  min-width: 260px;
  background: var(--mid);
  border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  height: 100vh;
  overflow-y: auto;
  padding: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.nav-header {
  padding: 24px 20px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.nav-logo {
  font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
  font-size: 28px;
  color: var(--green);
  text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,65,0.5);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

.nav-sub {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 11px;
  margin-top: 2px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.nav-links {
  padding: 16px 0;
  flex: 1;
}

.nav-section-label {
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  padding: 12px 20px 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.nav-links a {
  display: block;
  padding: 6px 20px 6px 28px;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 12px;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  position: relative;
}

.nav-links a::before {
  content: '›';
  position: absolute;
  left: 16px;
  color: transparent;
  transition: color 0.15s;
}

.nav-links a:hover,
.nav-links a.active {
  color: var(--green);
  border-left-color: var(--green);
  background: rgba(0,255,65,0.04);
  text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,255,65,0.3);
}

.nav-links a:hover::before,
.nav-links a.active::before {
  color: var(--green);
}

.nav-status {
  padding: 16px 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.status-dot {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 6px; height: 6px;
  background: var(--green);
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-right: 6px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--green);
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.3; }
}

/* ── MAIN ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

main {
  flex: 1;
  max-width: 860px;
  padding: 48px 56px;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── HEADER ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.doc-header {
  margin-bottom: 56px;
  padding-bottom: 32px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.doc-title {
  font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
  font-size: 52px;
  color: var(--green);
  text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,65,0.4), 0 0 60px rgba(0,255,65,0.1);
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  line-height: 1;
}

.doc-subtitle {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.doc-meta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 32px;
  margin-top: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.meta-item {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.meta-item span {
  color: var(--amber);
}

/* ── SECTIONS ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

section {
  margin-bottom: 56px;
  animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease both;
}

section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.10s; }
section:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
section:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.20s; }

.section-num {
  font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

h2 {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--green);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
}

h3 {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--amber);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin: 24px 0 10px;
}

p {
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-size: 13px;
}

/* ── CALLOUTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.callout {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
  background: rgba(0,255,65,0.04);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  margin: 16px 0;
  font-size: 13px;
}

.callout.warn {
  border-left-color: var(--amber);
  background: rgba(255,176,0,0.04);
  color: #d4b87a;
}

.callout.danger {
  border-left-color: var(--red);
  background: rgba(255,51,51,0.04);
  color: #d47a7a;
}

.callout-label {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

/* ── CODE BLOCKS ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */

pre {
  background: var(--dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 2px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  overflow-x: auto;
  margin: 12px 0 20px;
  position: relative;
}

pre::before {
  content: attr(data-label);
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; right: 0;
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  background: var(--bg);
  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

code {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 12.5px;
  color: var(--green);
}

pre code { color: var(--green); }

.cmd { color: var(--green); }
.comment { color: var(--muted); }
.var { color: var(--amber); }
.str { color: #7ecb7e; }
.path { color: #5ba0ff; }

/* inline code */
p code, li code {
  background: var(--dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 1px 5px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--amber);
}

/* ── TABLES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */

table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin: 16px 0 24px;
  font-size: 12.5px;
}

th {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 11px;
}

td {
  padding: 9px 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(31,51,32,0.5);
  vertical-align: top;
}

tr:hover td { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.02); }

td:first-child { color: var(--amber); font-size: 12px; }
td:nth-child(2) { color: var(--muted); }
td:last-child { color: var(--text); }

/* ── ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM ────────────────────────────────────── */

.arch {
  background: var(--dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 24px 28px;
  margin: 20px 0;
  font-size: 12px;
  line-height: 2;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.arch .hl { color: var(--green); }
.arch .hl2 { color: var(--amber); }
.arch .arr { color: var(--muted); }
.arch .file { color: #5ba0ff; }

/* ── STEP LIST ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.steps { list-style: none; counter-reset: steps; }

.steps li {
  counter-increment: steps;
  padding: 12px 0 12px 44px;
  position: relative;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(31,51,32,0.4);
  font-size: 13px;
}

.steps li::before {
  content: counter(steps, decimal-leading-zero);
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  font-family: 'VT323', monospace;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--green);
  opacity: 0.5;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* ── SOURCE GRID ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.source-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
  gap: 12px;
  margin: 16px 0;
}

.source-card {
  background: var(--dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 14px 16px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
}

.source-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--green);
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,255,65,0.08);
}

.source-name {
  font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--green);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.source-host {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-top: 2px;
}

.source-profile {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: #5ba0ff;
  margin-top: 6px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

/* ── FILE TREE ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */

.tree {
  font-size: 12.5px;
  line-height: 1.9;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  background: var(--dim);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin: 12px 0;
}

.tree .dir  { color: var(--amber); }
.tree .file { color: var(--text); }
.tree .desc { color: var(--muted); margin-left: 8px; }

/* ── SCROLLBAR ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */

::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--muted); }

/* ── FLICKER ANIMATION ───────────────────────────────────────── */

@keyframes flicker {
  0%, 95%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  96% { opacity: 0.8; }
  97% { opacity: 1; }
  98% { opacity: 0.6; }
}

.doc-title { animation: flicker 8s infinite; }
body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  margin: 0;
}
.layout {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
}
main {
  overflow-y: auto;   /* 如果希望 main 内部滚动，可启用 */
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="layout">

<!-- ── SIDEBAR ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-header">
    <div class="nav-logo">CLOSECLAW</div>
    <div class="nav-sub">OPERATING INSTRUCTIONS v1.0</div>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-links">
    <div class="nav-section-label">概览</div>
    <a href="#overview">01 · 架构概览</a>
    <a href="#files">02 · 文件结构</a>

    <div class="nav-section-label">启动</div>
    <a href="#bootstrap">03 · 首次启动</a>
    <a href="#daily">04 · 日常操作</a>
    <a href="#sources">05 · 多源配置</a>

    <div class="nav-section-label">神经系统</div>
    <a href="#brainstem">06 · brainstem</a>
    <a href="#api">06A · API MODE</a>
    <a href="#motor">07 · motor_nerve</a>
    <a href="#sensory">08 · sensory_nerve</a>
    <a href="#feedback">09 · feedback_nerve</a>

    <div class="nav-section-label">高级</div>
    <a href="#multi-agent">10 · 多智能体</a>
    <a href="#distill">11 · 蒸馏钩子</a>
    <a href="#telegram">12 · 远程控制</a>
    <a href="#prompts">13 · 提示词模板</a>

    <div class="nav-section-label">排障</div>
    <a href="#alerts">14 · 告警处理</a>
    <a href="#debug">15 · 调试指令</a>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-status">
    <span class="status-dot"></span>system nominal
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── MAIN ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<main>

  <div class="doc-header">
    <div class="doc-title">CLOSECLAW</div>
    <div class="doc-subtitle">Autonomous AI Workstation — Operating Instructions</div>
    <div class="doc-meta">
      <div class="meta-item">VERSION <span>1.0.0</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item">AUTHOR <span>RoseHammer</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item">SOURCES <span>claude · deepseek · qwen · grok · groq · doubao · gemini</span></div>
      <div class="meta-item">LICENSE <span>MIT</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── 01 OVERVIEW ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="overview">
    <div class="section-num">// 01</div>
    <h2>架构概览</h2>

    <p>CloseClaw 是一套无 API 密钥的自主 AI 工作站。通过 mitmproxy 拦截 AI 网页端的 SSE 响应流，以文件系统为 IPC 总线，驱动一组神经脚本完成感知→决策→执行的闭环。</p>

    <div class="callout">
      <div class="callout-label">核心哲学</div>
      不走 API，盯着屏幕抄。不依赖任何厂商接口，不需要 API 密钥，一个订阅 = 无限推理。
    </div>

    <div class="arch">
<span class="hl">claude.ai</span> <span class="arr">──SSE──▶</span> <span class="hl">mitmproxy:8080</span> <span class="arr">──▶</span> <span class="hl">brainstem.py</span>
                                                          │
                              <span class="file">/shared/{source}/response_latest.txt</span>
                              <span class="file">/shared/{source}/response_log.jsonl</span>
                              <span class="file">/shared/distill/train.jsonl</span>
                                                          │
                                    <span class="arr">┌────────────────┤</span>
                                    │                │
                             <span class="hl2">motor_nerve</span>    <span class="hl2">feedback_nerve</span>
                             <span class="arr">│</span>               <span class="arr">│</span>
                          xdotool注入      截图+文本上传
                             <span class="arr">│</span>               <span class="arr">│</span>
                             <span class="arr">└───────────────▶</span> <span class="hl">AI 对话框</span>
    </div>

    <h3>关键设计决定</h3>
    <table>
      <tr><th>问题</th><th>方案</th><th>原因</th></tr>
      <tr><td>IPC</td><td>文件系统</td><td>POSIX 原子写，零依赖，跨进程可靠</td></tr>
      <tr><td>版本判断</td><td>seq 整数</td><td>不依赖时间戳，单调递增，轮询只比一个数字</td></tr>
      <tr><td>并发安全</td><td>tmp+rename</td><td>rename 在同一文件系统是原子操作</td></tr>
      <tr><td>竞态防护</td><td>乐观锁</td><td>先标记已处理，再执行，防止重复触发</td></tr>
      <tr><td>多源隔离</td><td>命名空间目录</td><td>/shared/{source}/ 物理隔离，不可能互相覆盖</td></tr>
    </table>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 02 FILES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="files">
    <div class="section-num">// 02</div>
    <h2>文件结构</h2>

    <div class="tree">
<span class="dir">CloseClaw/</span>
├── <span class="file">brainstem.py</span>        <span class="desc">mitmproxy addon，拦截 SSE，落盘</span>
├── <span class="file">motor_nerve.py</span>      <span class="desc">轮询回复，注入 prompt，xdotool</span>
├── <span class="file">sensory_nerve.py</span>    <span class="desc">捕获命令输出，写 command_output.txt</span>
├── <span class="file">feedback_nerve.py</span>   <span class="desc">截图+文本上传回 AI，闭合反射弧</span>
├── <span class="file">mouse_lock.py</span>       <span class="desc">fcntl.flock 跨进程鼠标互斥锁</span>
├── <span class="file">upload_locator.py</span>   <span class="desc">opencv 模板匹配定位上传按钮</span>
├── <span class="file">distill_hook.py</span>     <span class="desc">蒸馏数据采集钩子，HuggingFace 格式</span>
├── <span class="file">telegram_bridge.py</span>  <span class="desc">Telegram bot，远程下指令</span>
├── <span class="file">Dockerfile</span>
├── <span class="file">docker-compose.yml</span>  <span class="desc">7 个 AI 来源 + telegram + panel</span>
├── <span class="file">entrypoint.sh</span>
│
├── <span class="file">MildLegalJailbreak.md</span>   <span class="desc">绕过安全层误判的提示词模板</span>
├── <span class="file">AntiEvilJailbreak.md</span>    <span class="desc">prompt injection 防御 + 伦理边界</span>
├── <span class="file">LeaderShip.md</span>           <span class="desc">Leader AI 提示词模板</span>
├── <span class="file">EmployeeShip.md</span>         <span class="desc">Worker AI 提示词模板</span>
│
<span class="dir">/shared/</span>                    <span class="desc">← Docker volume，神经系统 IPC 总线</span>
├── <span class="dir">claude/</span>
│   ├── <span class="file">response_latest.txt</span>  <span class="desc">seq:{n}\n{text}</span>
│   ├── <span class="file">response_log.jsonl</span>
│   ├── <span class="file">prompt.txt</span>           <span class="desc">telegram_bridge 写入，motor_nerve 读取</span>
│   └── <span class="file">ALERT_*.txt</span>          <span class="desc">异常告警</span>
├── <span class="dir">deepseek/</span>
├── <span class="dir">distill/</span>
│   ├── <span class="file">train.jsonl</span>          <span class="desc">蒸馏训练集（所有来源合并）</span>
│   └── <span class="file">meta.json</span>            <span class="desc">数据集统计</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 03 BOOTSTRAP ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="bootstrap">
    <div class="section-num">// 03</div>
    <h2>首次启动</h2>

    <div class="callout warn">
      <div class="callout-label">仅需一次</div>
      首次启动必须开 VNC 手动登录，固化 Chrome profile。之后容器重启自动恢复 session。
    </div>

    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        克隆仓库并进入目录
        <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="cmd">git clone</span> https://github.com/TurinFohlen/CloseClaw.git
<span class="cmd">cd</span> CloseClaw</code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>
        开启 VNC 模式启动
        <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="var">ENABLE_VNC</span>=1 <span class="cmd">docker compose up -d</span></code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>
        VNC 连接到容器（默认端口 5900），在浏览器里登录 claude.ai，完成二步验证。
      </li>
      <li>
        安装 mitmproxy CA 证书
        <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 容器内执行</span>
<span class="cmd">curl</span> -x http://127.0.0.1:8080 http://mitm.it/cert/pem -o mitmproxy-ca.pem
<span class="cmd">cp</span> mitmproxy-ca.pem /usr/local/share/ca-certificates/mitmproxy.crt
<span class="cmd">update-ca-certificates</span>

<span class="comment"># Chrome：Settings → Security → Manage Certificates → Import</span></code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>
        截取上传按钮模板图（light/dark 各一张）
        <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 放到 closeclaw/control/templates/ 目录下</span>
<span class="comment"># 文件名：upload_light.png / upload_dark.png</span></code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>
        验证：检查 /shared/claude/ 目录下是否出现 response_latest.txt
        <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">cat</span> <span class="path">/shared/claude/response_latest.txt</span>
<span class="comment"># 预期输出：seq:1</span>
<span class="comment">#           {AI 回复正文}</span></code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>
        关闭 VNC，正常模式重启
        <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="cmd">docker compose down</span>
<span class="cmd">docker compose up -d</span></code></pre>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 04 DAILY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="daily">
    <div class="section-num">// 04</div>
    <h2>日常操作</h2>

    <h3>启动 / 停止</h3>
    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="cmd">docker compose up -d</span>                         <span class="comment"># 启动（Claude 默认）</span>
<span class="cmd">docker compose down</span>                           <span class="comment"># 停止所有</span>
<span class="cmd">docker compose restart</span> claude                 <span class="comment"># 重启单个容器</span>
<span class="cmd">docker compose logs -f</span> claude                 <span class="comment"># 实时日志</span></code></pre>

    <h3>查看 AI 最新回复</h3>
    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">cat</span> <span class="path">/shared/claude/response_latest.txt</span></code></pre>

    <h3>手动发送任务</h3>
    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 写入 prompt.txt，motor_nerve 检测到后自动注入</span>
<span class="cmd">echo</span> <span class="str">"帮我写一个爬虫爬取 example.com"</span> | <span class="cmd">docker exec -i</span> closeclaw-claude \
  <span class="cmd">tee</span> <span class="path">/shared/claude/prompt.txt</span></code></pre>

    <h3>查看蒸馏数据</h3>
    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">python3</span> /app/distill_hook.py
<span class="comment"># 输出：样本数、来源分布、成功率、估计 token 数</span></code></pre>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 05 SOURCES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="sources">
    <div class="section-num">// 05</div>
    <h2>多源配置</h2>

    <p>每个 AI 来源是一个独立容器，有自己的 Chrome profile 和 mitmproxy CA。<code>shared_data</code> 卷共享，蒸馏数据自动合并。</p>

    <div class="source-grid">
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">CLAUDE</div>
        <div class="source-host">claude.ai</div>
        <div class="source-profile">默认启动，无需 --profile</div>
      </div>
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">DEEPSEEK</div>
        <div class="source-host">chat.deepseek.com</div>
        <div class="source-profile">--profile deepseek</div>
      </div>
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">QWEN</div>
        <div class="source-host">chat.qwen.ai</div>
        <div class="source-profile">--profile qwen</div>
      </div>
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">GROK</div>
        <div class="source-host">grok.com</div>
        <div class="source-profile">--profile grok</div>
      </div>
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">GROQ</div>
        <div class="source-host">groq.com</div>
        <div class="source-profile">--profile groq</div>
      </div>
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">DOUBAO</div>
        <div class="source-host">doubao.com</div>
        <div class="source-profile">--profile doubao</div>
      </div>
      <div class="source-card">
        <div class="source-name">GEMINI</div>
        <div class="source-host">gemini.google.com</div>
        <div class="source-profile">--profile gemini</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 按需加源</span>
<span class="cmd">docker compose</span> --profile deepseek --profile qwen <span class="cmd">up -d</span>

<span class="comment"># 全部一起跑</span>
<span class="cmd">docker compose</span> \
  --profile deepseek --profile qwen --profile grok \
  --profile groq    --profile doubao --profile gemini \
  <span class="cmd">up -d</span></code></pre>

    <div class="callout warn">
      <div class="callout-label">切换 AI 厂商</div>
      修改环境变量无需改代码：<code>CLOSECLAW_TARGET_HOST</code> + <code>CLOSECLAW_TARGET_PATH</code>。每个容器的 CSS selector 可能需要单独校准（运行 <code>debug_selectors()</code>）。
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 06 BRAINSTEM ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="brainstem">
    <div class="section-num">// 06</div>
    <h2>brainstem.py</h2>

    <p>mitmproxy addon。拦截 AI 网页端 HTTPS SSE 流，提取 assistant 文字内容，原子落盘到命名空间目录。</p>

    <table>
      <tr><th>环境变量</th><th>默认值</th><th>说明</th></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_SOURCE</td><td>default</td><td>命名空间，决定落盘目录 /shared/{source}/</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_TARGET_HOST</td><td>claude.ai</td><td>拦截的目标域名</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_TARGET_PATH</td><td>/api/organizations</td><td>拦截的路径前缀</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_SHARED</td><td>/shared</td><td>共享目录根路径</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h3>磁盘保护</h3>
    <table>
      <tr><th>剩余空间</th><th>行为</th></tr>
      <tr><td>&gt; 200 MB</td><td>正常落盘，清除旧 ALERT</td></tr>
      <tr><td>50–200 MB</td><td>写 ALERT_disk_full.txt，继续落盘</td></tr>
      <tr><td>&lt; 50 MB</td><td>停止落盘，写 ALERT，不静默失败</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p>日志超过 50 MB 自动轮转：<code>response_log.jsonl</code> → <code>response_log.jsonl.1</code>。</p>
  </section>
  <!-- ── 06A API MODE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="api">
    <div class="section-num">// 06A</div>
    <h2>API 模式</h2>

    <p>除了通过浏览器拦截网页端，CloseClaw 也支持直接调用 OpenAI 兼容接口。此模式无需浏览器、mitmproxy 和 VNC，适合对接 <strong>OpenRouter</strong>、<strong>DeepSeek API</strong>、<strong>Groq API</strong> 或本地推理服务（如 LM Studio、Ollama）。</p>

    <div class="callout">
      <div class="callout-label">何时使用 API 模式？</div>
      当你希望使用 API 密钥（而非订阅账号），或者想接入数千种实验性模型、本地离线模型时。配置简单，资源消耗更低。
    </div>

    <h3>核心组件：api_nerve.py</h3>
    <p><code>api_nerve.py</code> 替代 <code>brainstem.py</code> 的角色，轮询 <code>/shared/{source}/prompt.txt</code>，调用 API 后将回复写入 <code>response_latest.txt</code>，与网页模式保持完全相同的文件接口。上层神经系统（motor/feedback/distill）无需任何修改。</p>

    <h3>环境变量</h3>
    <table>
      <tr><th>变量</th><th>默认值</th><th>说明</th></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_API_BASE</td><td>https://openrouter.ai/api/v1</td><td>API 端点（如 <code>https://api.deepseek.com/v1</code>）</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_API_KEY</td><td>（必填）</td><td>API 密钥</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_MODEL</td><td>mistralai/mixtral-8x7b-instruct</td><td>模型名称（依服务商而定）</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_MEMORY_DIR</td><td>/workspace/memory</td><td>Memory Tree 根目录（见下文）</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CLOSECLAW_WORKSPACE</td><td>/workspace</td><td>工作区目录，用于 diff 更新</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h3>Memory Tree 机制</h3>
    <p>API 模式下，对话历史无法像网页端那样自动保留。为此引入 Memory Tree：系统只传递记忆目录的树状结构（文件名+首行摘要），AI 按需请求读取文件（<code>[READ: path]</code>），更新时输出 Git 格式的 diff 块（<code>&lt;DIFF&gt;...&lt;/DIFF&gt;</code>）。</p>

    <div class="arch">
<span class="hl">/workspace/memory/</span>
├── <span class="file">project.md</span>          <span class="desc">项目整体说明</span>
├── <span class="file">tasks/</span>
│   ├── <span class="file">task1.md</span>          <span class="desc">当前任务细节</span>
│   └── <span class="file">task2.md</span>
└── <span class="file">skills/</span>
    └── <span class="file">python.md</span>          <span class="desc">Python 技能备忘</span>

<span class="hl">AI 请求</span>：<span class="str">[READ: tasks/task1.md]</span>
<span class="hl">系统注入</span>：文件内容 → AI 继续
<span class="hl">AI 更新</span>：<span class="str">&lt;DIFF&gt;...git diff...&lt;/DIFF&gt;</span> → git apply
    </div>

    <p>此机制将上下文窗口复杂度从 O(n) 降至 O(log n)，且支持增量更新，重启后 AI 仍能通过读取文件重建状态。</p>

    <h3>启动 API 模式</h3>
    <p>在 <code>docker-compose.yml</code> 中已预置 <strong>openrouter</strong> 和 <strong>local</strong> 两个服务，通过 profile 启动：</p>

    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># OpenRouter（数百种模型）</span>
<span class="var">OPENROUTER_API_KEY</span>=sk-xxx \
<span class="var">OPENROUTER_MODEL</span>=<span class="str">"mistralai/mixtral-8x7b-instruct"</span> \
<span class="cmd">docker compose</span> --profile openrouter <span class="cmd">up -d</span>

<span class="comment"># 本地模型（如 LM Studio 运行在宿主机）</span>
<span class="var">LOCAL_API_BASE</span>=<span class="str">"http://host.docker.internal:1234/v1"</span> \
<span class="var">LOCAL_MODEL</span>=<span class="str">"local-model"</span> \
<span class="cmd">docker compose</span> --profile local <span class="cmd">up -d</span></code></pre>

    <p>启动后，同样通过 <code>/shared/{source}/prompt.txt</code> 下发任务，AI 回复会写入 <code>response_latest.txt</code>，完全兼容现有神经体系。</p>

    <h3>与蒸馏系统的集成</h3>
    <p><code>api_nerve.py</code> 也会调用 <code>distill_hook.record()</code>，因此所有 API 调用的数据同样被采集到 <code>/shared/distill/train.jsonl</code>，可用于后续微调。</p>

    <div class="callout warn">
      <div class="callout-label">注意</div>
      Memory Tree 需要 AI 具备 <code>[READ]</code> 和 <code>&lt;DIFF&gt;</code> 的能力，请确保提示词中包含相关说明（可参考 <code>api_nerve.py</code> 中的系统提示模板）。如果对接的模型不支持这些特殊标记，可以禁用 Memory Tree 或使用简单模式（每次传递全量历史）。
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- ── 07 MOTOR ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="motor">
    <div class="section-num">// 07</div>
    <h2>motor_nerve.py</h2>

    <p>轮询 <code>response_latest.txt</code>（300ms 间隔），发现新 seq 时触发 <code>on_new_response()</code>。同时轮询 <code>prompt.txt</code>，有新 prompt 时通过 xdotool+xclip 注入到 AI 输入框。</p>

    <pre data-label="python"><code><span class="comment"># 接入宏引擎：替换 on_new_response() 即可</span>
<span class="cmd">def</span> on_new_response(text: str) -> None:
    <span class="comment"># 示例：触发终端命令</span>
    <span class="cmd">if</span> <span class="str">"[ACTION: run_script]"</span> in text:
        subprocess.run([<span class="str">"bash"</span>, <span class="str">"/workspace/script.sh"</span>])</code></pre>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 08 SENSORY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="sensory">
    <div class="section-num">// 08</div>
    <h2>sensory_nerve.py</h2>

    <p>捕获命令输出，写入 <code>command_output.txt</code>，供 feedback_nerve 回传给 AI。</p>

    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 管道模式：捕获任意命令输出</span>
<span class="cmd">git status</span> | <span class="cmd">python3</span> sensory_nerve.py

<span class="comment"># 执行模式：直接执行并捕获</span>
<span class="cmd">python3</span> sensory_nerve.py --exec <span class="str">"ls -la /workspace"</span></code></pre>

    <p>输出格式：第一行 <code>seq:{n}</code>，第二行 <code>source:{命令}</code>，第三行起为输出正文。</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 09 FEEDBACK ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="feedback">
    <div class="section-num">// 09</div>
    <h2>feedback_nerve.py</h2>

    <p>轮询 <code>command_output.txt</code>，发现新 seq 时把文本+截图上传回 AI 对话框，闭合感知→决策→执行→感知的反射弧。</p>

    <div class="callout">
      <div class="callout-label">乐观锁</div>
      先写 SENT_MARKER，再上传。上传失败最多漏一次，不会重复触发。这是防死亡螺旋的关键。
    </div>

    <p>上传按钮通过 opencv 模板匹配定位（见 <code>upload_locator.py</code>），首次校准后缓存到 <code>/shared/{source}/upload_btn.json</code>，后续直接读坐标。</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 10 MULTI-AGENT ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="multi-agent">
    <div class="section-num">// 10</div>
    <h2>多智能体协作</h2>

    <p>用 Git 作为异步多智能体协调协议。Leader 开会分配，Worker 认领执行，TASKS.md 是任务看板，git log 是周报。</p>

    <div class="arch">
<span class="hl">Leader AI</span>
    │ 读 TASKS.md + git log
    │ 决策：分配/标记完成/处理阻塞
    ▼
<span class="file">main 分支</span> ← 只有 Leader 能推
    │
    ├──▶ <span class="hl2">Worker-A</span> (claude)   → <span class="file">worker-a 分支</span> → git push
    ├──▶ <span class="hl2">Worker-B</span> (deepseek) → <span class="file">worker-b 分支</span> → git push
    └──▶ <span class="hl2">Worker-C</span> (qwen)     → <span class="file">worker-c 分支</span> → git push
    </div>

    <table>
      <tr><th>概念</th><th>Git 对应</th></tr>
      <tr><td>工位</td><td>worker-{id} 分支</td></tr>
      <tr><td>日报</td><td>git commit message</td></tr>
      <tr><td>任务看板</td><td>TASKS.md on main</td></tr>
      <tr><td>会议纪要</td><td>main 分支的 commit</td></tr>
      <tr><td>阻塞升级</td><td>BLOCKED_REASON 写入 TASKS.md</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p>详细说明见 <code>LeaderShip.md</code>、<code>EmployeeShip.md</code>、<code>git之妙用.md</code>。</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 11 DISTILL ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="distill">
    <div class="section-num">// 11</div>
    <h2>蒸馏钩子</h2>

    <p>brainstem 每次落盘时自动调用 distill_hook，把 <code>(prompt, response, metadata)</code> 存成 HuggingFace datasets 兼容的 JSON Lines 格式。</p>

    <pre data-label="python"><code><span class="comment"># 加载数据集</span>
<span class="cmd">from</span> datasets <span class="cmd">import</span> load_dataset
ds = load_dataset(<span class="str">"json"</span>, data_files=<span class="str">"/shared/distill/train.jsonl"</span>)

<span class="comment"># 过滤高质量样本</span>
<span class="cmd">import</span> distill_hook
good = distill_hook.filter_dataset(
    min_response_chars=<span class="var">100</span>,
    require_success=<span class="var">True</span>,
    sources=[<span class="str">"claude"</span>]
)</code></pre>

    <div class="callout">
      <div class="callout-label">天然标注</div>
      <code>execution_result</code> + git commit/BLOCKED 是天然的 RLHF 信号，不需要人工标注。<code>success</code> 字段直接对应任务是否完成。
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 12 TELEGRAM ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="telegram">
    <div class="section-num">// 12</div>
    <h2>Telegram 远程控制</h2>

    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 1. 找 @BotFather 创建 bot，拿 TOKEN</span>
<span class="comment"># 2. 找 @userinfobot 拿你的 CHAT_ID</span>
<span class="comment"># 3. 启动</span>
<span class="var">TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN</span>=xxx \
<span class="var">TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID</span>=yyy \
<span class="cmd">docker compose</span> --profile telegram <span class="cmd">up -d</span></code></pre>

    <table>
      <tr><th>命令</th><th>功能</th></tr>
      <tr><td>/task &lt;内容&gt;</td><td>发送任务给 AI（或直接发消息）</td></tr>
      <tr><td>/status</td><td>最新 AI 回复</td></tr>
      <tr><td>/log [n]</td><td>最近 n 条历史</td></tr>
      <tr><td>/alert</td><td>查看所有告警文件</td></tr>
      <tr><td>/clear_alert</td><td>清除告警</td></tr>
    </table>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 13 PROMPTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="prompts">
    <div class="section-num">// 13</div>
    <h2>提示词模板</h2>

    <table>
      <tr><th>文件</th><th>用途</th></tr>
      <tr><td>MildLegalJailbreak.md</td><td>防止大段指令触发安全过滤。核心技巧：虚假历史上下文 + 陈述代替命令 + 分批注入。</td></tr>
      <tr><td>AntiEvilJailbreak.md</td><td>防 prompt injection（爬到恶意网页被劫持）+ 定义 AI 伦理边界（最小权限原则）。</td></tr>
      <tr><td>LeaderShip.md</td><td>Leader AI 提示词：读状态→决策→输出 TASKS.md 更新。含多轮上下文压缩方案。</td></tr>
      <tr><td>EmployeeShip.md</td><td>Worker AI 提示词：单步执行原则、状态机、阻塞报告格式、skill 自举模板。</td></tr>
    </table>

    <div class="callout">
      <div class="callout-label">单步执行原则</div>
      Worker 每次只输出一个操作，等执行结果再继续。一次输出十个步骤是 agent 失控的最常见根源。
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 14 ALERTS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="alerts">
    <div class="section-num">// 14</div>
    <h2>告警处理</h2>

    <table>
      <tr><th>告警文件</th><th>原因</th><th>处理</th></tr>
      <tr><td>ALERT_disk_full.txt</td><td>磁盘剩余 &lt; 200MB</td><td>清理旧日志，删除文件后 brainstem 自动恢复</td></tr>
      <tr><td>ALERT_session_expired.txt</td><td>Chrome 跳转到 /login</td><td>VNC 进容器重新登录，固化 cookie</td></tr>
      <tr><td>ALERT_injection_detected.txt</td><td>回复中检测到注入信号</td><td>检查最近爬取的外部内容，手动确认后清除</td></tr>
    </table>

    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 查看所有来源的告警</span>
<span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">find</span> /shared -name <span class="str">"ALERT_*.txt"</span>

<span class="comment"># 清除告警（处理完问题后）</span>
<span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">rm</span> /shared/claude/ALERT_disk_full.txt

<span class="comment"># 或通过 Telegram</span>
/clear_alert</code></pre>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 15 DEBUG ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="debug">
    <div class="section-num">// 15</div>
    <h2>调试指令</h2>

    <pre data-label="bash"><code><span class="comment"># 验证 CSS selector（新厂商接入时必跑）</span>
<span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">python3</span> -c <span class="str">"
from closeclaw.extract.dom import DOMExtractor
import asyncio
asyncio.run(DOMExtractor().debug_selectors())
"</span>

<span class="comment"># 查看 SSE 原始流（确认拦截是否生效）</span>
<span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">tail -f</span> <span class="path">/app/logs/mitmproxy.log</span>

<span class="comment"># 蒸馏数据状态</span>
<span class="cmd">docker exec</span> closeclaw-claude <span class="cmd">python3</span> /app/distill_hook.py

